jade.webservice.dynamicClient
Class WSData

java.lang.Object
  jade.webservice.dynamicClient.WSData
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class WSData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Data container for input/output parameters/headers of DynamicCliet invocation.
The values are expressed with AbsObject. For JADE primitive value (eg. String, float,...) special methods wrap and dewrap automatically the value from and to AbsPrimitive

See Also:
DynamicClient, AbsObject, Serialized Form
